"ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014551, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "It is narrated that a man complained to the Holy Prophet (s) about colitis from which his brother had suffered. The Holy Prophet (s) instructed, “Tell your brother to drink a mixture of honey and hot water.” The next day, the man returned to the Holy Prophet (s) and informed that the prescription was not useful. The Holy Prophet (s) commented, “Allah is truthful, but your brother’s colon is not. Go back, give him the same drink, and recite on it <Surah Fateha> 7 times as prayer for God’s protection.” When the man left, the Holy Prophet (s) said to Imam Ali (a), “The brother of this man is hypocrite; therefore, the drink was not effective with him.”", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Riwaayat mein hai keh ek shakhs Hazrat Rasool-e-Khuda (s) ki khidmat mein haazir huwa aur apne bhai ke peyt dard ki shikaayat ki to Aan Hazrat (s) ne us se farmaaya apne bhai se kaho keh garam paani mein shahed (honey) ka sharbat bana kar peeye, woh shakhs chala gaya aur dusre din Aan Janaab (s) ki khidmat mein aaya aur arz kiya mai ne usey woh sharbat pilaaya hai koi afaaqah (faayeda) nahi huwa Hazrat (s) ne farmaya: Khuda ne sach farmaya aur tere bhai ke shikam ne jhoot bola. Jaawo usey phir se shahed (honey) ka sharbat do aur 7 martaba <Surah Fateha> padh kar peelawo jab woh shakhs chala gaya to Aan Hazrat (s) ne Hazrat Ali-e-Murtaza (a) se farmaaya: Ya Ali uska bhai munaafeqoon mein se hai is liye sharbat ne usey faayeda nahi pohonchaaya.", "UrduDescription": "روایت میں آیا ہے: ایک شخص حضرت رسول خدا ؐ کی خدمت میں حاضر ہوا اور اپنے بھائی کے پیٹ درد کی شکایت کی تو آنحضرتؐ نے اس سے فرمایا :اپنے بھائی سے کہو کہ گرم پانی میں شہد کا شربت بنا کر پیئے وہ شخص چلا گیا اوردوسرے دن حضرتؑ کی خدمت میں آیا اور عرض کیا: میں نے اسے وہ شربت پلایا ہے کوئی افاقہ نہیں ہوا حضرت ؐنے فرمایا ’’خدا نے سچ فرمایا اور تیرے بھائی کے شکم نے جھوٹ بولا۔‘‘جاؤ اسے شہد کا شربت دواور ۷ مرتبہ <سورۂ فاتحہ> پڑھ کر پلاؤ جب وہ شخص چلا گیا تو آنحضرتؐ نے حضرت علی المرتضیٰ ؑ سے فرمایا:یا علی ؑ! اس کا بھائی منافقوں میں سے ہے اس لئے اس شربت نے اسے فائدہ نہیں پہنچایا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": nu